        "eyebrow": "The Immigrant Gut",
        "headline": "Your bloating isn't a food problem. It's a bacterial extinction event inside your gut.",
        "subheadline": "You've cut dairy. Gluten. FODMAPs. Your diet gets smaller every year but the bloating never stops. That's because bloating isn't caused by what you eat — it's caused by the ancestral bacteria you lost. When those populations disappear, food that your grandmother digested effortlessly now ferments inside you like a bomb.",
        "cta_text": "End the Bloating — $34/mo",
